  "title": "Junior Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements<br /></p><p>Position: Senior Electrical Engineer</p><p>Education : Bachelor’s Degree in Electrical Engineering.<br /></p><p>Experience:</p><p>• Developing, reviewing, updating, modifying, and approving\nelectrical design plans and work schedules.</p><p>• Liaising with clients and other engineers to ensure\nprojects are completed to specifications.</p><p>• Establishing relationships with clients, vendors,\nsuppliers, other professionals, and expanding networks.</p><p>• Assist in the development of project proposals, budgets,\ncost standards and schedules. Should have good experience in pricing for the\nproject in Singapore.</p><p>• Manage a multi project workload as well as oversee the\ndesign work of other engineers and designers.</p><p>• Work with Engineers and Designers to prepare new drawings,\nmodify existing drawings, or create as-built documents.</p><p>• Provide technical support and support regional business\ndevelopment initiatives as a technical resource.</p><p>• Represent us professionally at all project related\nmeetings and inspections.<br /></p><p>Core Competencies</p><p>• Strong knowledge of the technical aspects of the\nelectrical engineering practice</p><p>• Thorough knowledge of all codes applicable to his/her\ndiscipline</p><p>• Critical thinking and problem solving</p><p>• Leadership and mentoring</p><p>• Project and resource management</p><p>• Problem solving/analysis</p><p>• Communication proficiency with team members and clients</p><p>• Experience with design software such as but not limited to\nAutoCAD, Revit, etc. will be added advantage.</p>",
